title: 208 Ponte Vedra Drive
body: Welcome to Champions Village and this beautiful Low Country inspired home. Champions Village is a natural gas community that sits directly on the 18th fairway of TPC Myrtle Beach. This 4 bedroom and 2 1/2 bath home features a first floor master bed and bath with a beautiful tiled shower, huge walk in closet, granite countertops throughout, LVP flooring in the living room and common areas, beautifully painted cabinets, stainless appliances (range, microwave, and dishwasher), and a big 2 car garage. The home is very energy efficient with R50 insulation in the ceilings, radiant barrier sheathing on the roof, a tankless hot water heater, and much more. Please do not miss your chance to see this well appointed home!

title: Shoals Landing, Lot 14
display_name: 354 Silver Anchor Drive, Lot 14, Columbia, SC 29212
body: New Construction by Great Southern Homes. Lot 14 Shoals Landing. Amelia D6 Floor plan with the Sunroom added! On the main level you'll find the MASTER BEDROOM with large walk-in closet, separate tub and walk-in shower, water closet and double vanity. The large kitchen sports painted ivory, Shaker style cabinets, 3 cm granite, stainless appliance package and pantry. The greatroom offers a gas log fireplace. You'll fall in love with the bright Sunroom that can also serve as a dining area. You'll also be pampered with the double garage and rear patio. Upstairs are Bedrooms 2 & 3, a full bath and loft area. The baths, laundry, foyer, kitchen, sunroom and greatroom are all finished with LVP (Luxury Vinyl Plank). The front exterior offers a craftsman styling with low maintenance vinyl siding and stone accents. The Honeywell Smart Home Automation System is included! You may opt to include our Residential Energy GUARANTEE! One year builder workmanship warranty and 10 structural warranty are included! The home is loaded with GreenSmart energy efficient features: radiant barrier attic sheathing, HERS testing & tankless water heater, energy efficient gas furnace and much, much more! You'll really appreciate the low utility bills you'll enjoy in our energy efficient homes! Fully landscaped with sod & sprinklers.

Two more nice sized BRs complete the lay-out along with the shared hall bath. Laundry room. Double garage with opener & covered patio/porch is great for outdoor entertaining! title: 59 Windy Lane
body: New raised beach home across from the marsh in Litchfield Breezes! Under construction. Great features of the home include tankless hotwater heater, 10' ceilings, crown molding, recessed lighting, hardwood flooring and more! Kitchen has granite countertops, tile backsplash, gas range, and stainless steel appliances. Cable and high speed internet are included in HOA. Sit on your front porch and enjoy breezes off beautiful Litchfield Creek. Litchfield is located just 70 miles for a day trip to historic Charleston, SC or 25 miles to the attractions of Myrtle Beach!
